data.name: RichTextBox1.Text
data.value: I, [Your Name], pledge to drive responsibly and adhere to all traffic laws. I understand the importance of prioritizing safety on the road, not only for myself but for the well-being of others. I commit to avoiding distractions, respecting speed limits, and being mindful of pedestrians and fellow drivers. By signing below, I affirm my dedication to being a responsible and courteous driver.
